name: Hollow Pixels 3 - Libel
description:
The fauna and flora of Hollow Pixels is unique. Composed of exclusively black and white pixels within a 100x100 px habitat, you won’t find the same living being twice nonetheless. 
Here is a flying cable, or a dragon fly-fish, or a flower. Let’s call it Libel. 

IG&Twitter:  @dacosta_works
